elements.name: Como autor creo un post, y despues le agrego un tag

steps.name: I navigate to page "<HOST>" "ghost/#/signin"
I login with credentials "<USERNAME>" "<PASSWORD>"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "logged"
I wait for 2 seconds
I go to tag list
I go to new tag form
I send a signal to user 2 containing "creating tag"
I wait for 2 seconds
I create a tag with name "$name_1"
I save the tag
I send a signal to user 2 containing "tag created"
I wait for 2 seconds
I go to new post form
I send a signal to user 2 containing "creating"
I wait for 2 seconds
I create a post with title "$name_2" and content "$string_1"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "posting"
I wait for 2 seconds
I post the post
I send a signal to user 2 containing "post created"
I wait for a signal containing "checking" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "checked notag" for 30 seconds
I return to posts list
I select the listed post with name "$$name_2"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "editing"
I wait for 2 seconds
I choose the tag "$$name_1"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "tagging"
I wait for 2 seconds
I update the post
I send a signal to user 2 containing "post tagged"

name: Crear un post sin tag, revisar que el usuario lector no vea tags en este post, agregar un tag, y revisar que el usuario lector pueda verlo
